{
  "stem": "21349.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we came to the prison they told us, wait here, we have to register you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what they did with the Jews when they send them to prison and afterwards to concentration camp, they photographed them from three sides.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They want to find out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do they have this hook nose?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do they have these-- nose-- these ears which are detached?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Do they have this skull, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do they have these kind of ears, of eyes, all kind of things?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took all kinds of measurements.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They photographed us from three sides.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they say, take everything out of your pockets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were very organized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That I must say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Nazis were very organized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wrote down every little thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's why we have so many names now of people in concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Otherwise we wouldn't have any names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they wrote down you had a watch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had pot money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Pot money means your-- Wallet?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--purse a purse.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had so much money in there, you see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these things all that they put down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put it in, and they left in their safe there or something like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they said, now go upstairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they brought us into different cells.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Me, they brought into cell number 99.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I thought it was a good name, a good number, you see, 99.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And there were about 15 boys in this cell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a small room, maybe like this size, or maybe smaller.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and there was only a window on top.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was only a wooden table and wooden planks, no mattresses actually.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In-- in the door there was a window.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And through this window they handed out some food sometimes.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
